<! [CDATA[
 Quest Software Logo
Quest Software, also known as Quest, is a privately held software company headquartered in Aliso Viejo, California, United States with 53 offices in 24 countries. The company was founded in 1987. The company is known for Toad, a product used by database professionals, in addition to other offerings for Microsoft Azure cloud management, software as a service, security, workforce mobility, data-driven insight, and backup and recovery. Quest Software was acquired by Dell in 2012, for $2.
You can download theQuestlogo on full-version of the page.
